This is another big win for North Carolina.
 
@Novartis is opening a new manufacturing facility in Morrisville, which will bring more jobs to NC &amp; help strengthen our state’s reputation as a center for innovation.
 
Thank you to Novartis for continuing to invest in NC’s future!

